496
00:45:02,421 --> 00:45:03,763
Good night.

497
00:45:17,620 --> 00:45:18,665
Would you stop?

498
00:45:23,730 --> 00:45:27,591
Boy, I believe I drank too much coffee.

499
00:45:31,154 --> 00:45:34,350
