512
00:47:46,692 --> 00:47:48,317
You didn't just happen by.

513
00:47:50,629 --> 00:47:52,253
Why not?

514
00:48:18,402 --> 00:48:21,185
Go on and take a load off your feet.

515
00:48:45,184 --> 00:48:47,159
You ought to get yourself a wife.

516
00:48:47,519 --> 00:48:48,828
Yeah.

517
00:48:49,055 --> 00:48:50,811
