Just a garden patch and a pasture.

525
00:49:21,373 --> 00:49:23,641
I was sick at planting time.

526
00:49:24,603 --> 00:49:25,947
So...

527
00:49:28,059 --> 00:49:30,295
Ed, how you feeling now?

528
00:49:33,019 --> 00:49:34,035
