529
00:49:35,868 --> 00:49:37,972
You're acting queer.

530
00:49:46,137 --> 00:49:49,652
Well, you and me ain't been
just real good friends lately.

531
00:49:50,586 --> 00:49:53,554
That's not your fault,
you understand that.

532
00:49:55,803 --> 00:49:57,360
You hear talk, though.

533
00:49:59,321 --> 00:50:00,749
Talk?

534
00:50:04,408 --> 00:50:06,547
People tell you things.

535
00:50:13,784 --> 00:50:15,792
