543
00:50:52,852 --> 00:50:54,891
That's just talk probably.

544
00:50:58,739 --> 00:51:02,417
Jim Cummins. He say anything else?

545
00:51:02,771 --> 00:51:06,480
Nope. No, that was it, basically.

546
00:51:16,466 --> 00:51:18,766
