and lung congestions.

612
00:59:59,554 --> 01:00:02,716
Insomnia stained
his eye sockets like soot.

613
01:00:03,521 --> 01:00:06,390
He read auguries in
the snarled intestines of chickens...

614
01:00:07,552 --> 01:00:10,967
...or the blow of cat hair
released to the wind.

615
01:00:11,744 --> 01:00:16,500
And the omens promised bad luck,
which moated and dungeoned him.

616
01:00:56,508 --> 01:00:58,963
How come it's you
that's gotta do all the chores?

617
01:00:59,132 --> 01:01:03,190
Charley and Bob pay extry to Martha
so that they don't have to.

618
01:01:04,443 --> 01:01:06,417
It still don't seem fair.

619
01:01:12,922 --> 01:01:14,383
Martha.

620
01:01:16,057 --> 01:01:18,545
Well, look what the cat dragged in.

621
01:01:23,162 --> 01:01:24,371
You come from Kentucky?

622
01:01:27,639 --> 01:01:31,317
Why do you have your head in a hole,
Martha?

623
01:01:34,232 --> 01:01:37,811
