a few months ago.

624
01:01:39,320 --> 01:01:40,531
Cover the kettle, Ida.

625
01:01:45,591 --> 01:01:47,795
And what did you and Dick
get in a scrape about?

626
01:01:51,511 --> 01:01:55,340
Well, he tampered
with my daddy's wife...

627
01:01:55,510 --> 01:01:58,739
...while a pork chop
burned on the skillet...

628
01:01:58,902 --> 01:02:00,362
...so I shot at him.

629
01:02:05,238 --> 01:02:09,461
Ida! Do not stick your thumb
in the cream when you skim it.

630
01:02:10,580 --> 01:02:15,565
His chicanery and his philandering ways...

631
01:02:15,732 --> 01:02:17,619
...has instigated such malice.

632
01:02:17,781 --> 01:02:21,556
He's a yellow snake in the grass
and he can't be trusted, Martha.

633
01:02:24,339 --> 01:02:27,568
Dick told me a complete other version
of that affray.

634
01:02:28,978 --> 01:02:31,534
Wood Hite's downstairs.

635
01:02:32,211 --> 01:02:33,837
You mean he's here?

636
01:02:36,498 --> 01:02:39,083
Yeah, he come in late last night.

637
01:02:42,642 --> 01:02:43,623
Hey, simmer down!

638
01:02:43,793 --> 01:02:48,169
Don't get into a fracas up there, you boys!
I've got breakfast almost ready.

639
01:04:53,701 --> 01:04:55,805
