663
01:07:50,484 --> 01:07:53,037
Blessed are the poor in spirit...

664
01:07:53,206 --> 01:07:55,375
...for theirs is the kingdom of heaven.

665
01:07:56,755 --> 01:08:02,091
Blessed are them that mourn,
for they shall be comforted.

666
01:08:04,145 --> 01:08:06,002
Blessed are the...

667
01:08:09,394 --> 01:08:10,856
Meek.

668
01:08:13,043 --> 01:08:14,799
Blessed are the meek.

